title: Up First briefing: U.S. conducts airstrikes on militants in Iraq; 2023 U.S. union wins
description: President Biden orders retaliatory strikes against militants in Iraq after three U.S. servicemembers were injured. A look at the state of U.S. unions after several big 2023 wins.

title: 276 Indians stuck in a French airport for a human trafficking probe arrive in India
description: A charter plane that was grounded in France for a human trafficking investigation arrived in India with 276 Indians aboard early Tuesday.

title: Biden orders strike on Iranian-aligned group after 3 U.S. troops injured in Iraq
description: President Joe Biden ordered the U.S. military to carry out retaliatory strikes against Iranian-backed militia groups after three U.S. servicemembers were injured in a drone attack in northern Iraq.
